---
title: Pork Sausages & Pepper Red Wine Jus with Cheesy Crushed Potatoes & Dijon Corn Slaw
description: These aren’t any ordinary silly sausages, they’re herby pork sausages coated in a punchy peppercorn red wine jus. If you look closer, that slaw isn’t just colourful but packed full of flavour from dijon mayo. It’s another standout dinner that we can’t get enough of.
